# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Neural Genome — Public Repo .gitignore
#
# This repo is the public face of the Neural Genome moonshot.
# Only mission-critical, externally-meaningful content is pushed.
# Agent-process and internal-scaffolding files stay private.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ═══ PROCESS / AGENT-INTERNAL DOCS (PRIVATE) ═══
# Agent operating manuals stay private. WIKI.md is the project state-registry
# index (short, pointer-only) — kept public so readers can follow project state
# and so the §3.5 "patched-same-commit" invariant is enforceable via git.
CLAUDE.md
ROUNDTABLE_STATE.md
*_HANDOFF.md
*_NOTES.md

# Codex review artifacts — private senior-review scratch
codex_*.md
codex_*.txt
codex_*.log
*_REVIEW.md
*_AUDIT.md
.codex/
codex-output/
reviews/

# Claude Code runtime state (scheduled-tasks lockfiles, etc.)
.claude/
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/settings.local.json

# Heartbeat / session scratch
heartbeat_*.md
session_*.md

# In-progress / draft preregs (locked preregs ARE public)
research/prereg/drafts/
research/prereg/*.draft.md

# ═══ MODEL WEIGHTS & LARGE BINARY ARTIFACTS ═══
*.bin
*.safetensors
*.gguf
*.ggml
*.pt
*.pth
*.onnx
*.npz
*.npy
*.pkl
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.parquet

# HuggingFace cache (if accidentally placed inside repo)
.cache/
models_cache/
hf_cache/

# Feature extraction caches (intermediate, reproducible from code+data)
results/cache/

# Large activation dumps / atlas artifacts — live outside git
activations/
atlas_dumps/
*.activations
*.tensors

# ═══ PYTHON ═══
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
*.egg
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.tox/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
.env
.env.local

